high_descs: turn around and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room on the right corner
grab a tomato out of the fridge there
turn around and walk over to the right side of the room where the stove is, and look up to face the microwave a bit
place the tomato inside of the microwave, turn on the microwave to cook the tomato, once it is done take it back out
look downwards a bit, and turn around to walk back over to the fridge in the left side far corner of the room
place the tomato inside of the fridge there
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved tomato inside of the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge ahead.
Open the fridge, take the tomato from inside, and close the fridge.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go to the stove, they look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it up, then take tomato out.
Turn around and go across the room to the wall, then turn right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Take the tomato out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and veer left, back to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge, to the right and in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge.
